                    </div>
                    <span>When you speak you want to get your point across. Karrass in an easy reading style sets out those rules of communication. If you know the rules you can have fun and respect when someone says "I saw it cheaper down the street" or "I will wash the dishes tomorrow".<P>This book is not just for the salesperson. The book is for everyone who wants to negotiate.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A great book; it really helped me.</div>
